## Proposed Changes (Priority Order)

### Phase 1: Critical Fixes (Make It Work)

#### [MODIFY] [.env.local](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/PassMeet/.env.local)
- Generate real `PASSMEET_AUTH_SECRET`
- Set real USDCx/USAD token IDs after token registration

#### [MODIFY] [PassMeetContext.tsx](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/PassMeet/src/context/PassMeetContext.tsx)
- Fix `buyTicket` to re-read `ticket_count` before computing `nextTicketId`
- Remove `version` field from manual record construction in `verifyEntry`
- Add better Shield wallet error handling

#### [MODIFY] [main.leo](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/PassMeet/contracts/passmeet_v1_7788/src/main.leo)
- Fix nullifier computation to include `owner` for privacy
- Verify `token_registry.aleo/transfer_private` return order

### Phase 2: Compliance Fixes (Meet Rules)

- Register real test tokens on testnet
- Test full payment flow with credits, USDCx, and USAD through Shield wallet
- Set up Pinata for IPFS metadata persistence
- Configure contracts on-chain (`configure_tokens`, `configure`)

### Phase 3: Quality Improvements

- Rename contract directories to match program names
- Add more tests
- Remove `orchids-visual-edits`
- Restrict `images.remotePatterns`
- Subscription feature enforcement or honest UI

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run existing tests: `npm run test:run`
- After fixes, add tests for [aleoRecords.ts](file:///c:/Users/BMSIT/PassMeet/src/lib/aleoRecords.ts) record parsing
- After fixes, add Shield wallet mock tests for `buyTicket` flow

### Manual Verification (Requires Shield Wallet Extension)
1. **Token Registration:** Register a test token via `token_registry.aleo`, verify token ID appears on-chain
2. **Shield Mint Flow:** Connect Shield wallet → Auth → Create event (free) → Mint ticket → Verify the entire flow completes without errors
3. **Paid Mint:** Create event with credits price → Buy ticket with credits → Verify payment reaches organizer
4. **Gate Verification:** Mint ticket → Go to Gate page → Verify entry → Confirm nullifier on-chain
5. **Subscription:** Subscribe with credits → Verify subscription mapping on-chain

